<p class="head">Sahara release notes</p>

<p class="subhead">
4.0 Sahara release for Open Source publication
</p>
<ul>
<li>Fixed a user delete bug</li>
<li>Bundled harvester and web control panel in one package.</li>
</ul>

<p class="subhead">
3.0 Sahara release
</p>
<ul>
<li>Installation for Red Hat Fedora Core 6 (for KNAW)</li>
<li>Installation for SuSE (for DRIVER)</li>
</ul>

<p class="subhead">
2.0 Sahara release for pre-production for EduRep and DAREnet
</p>

<ul>
<li>Login/account management and authentication more secure</li>
<li>Introduced domains and repositorygroups</li>
<li>Administration split over multiple screens</li>
<li>Admin account</li>
<li>Accounts can manage one domain</li>
<li>Target types for FAST FDS and Lucene</li>
<li>Secured all access via SSL</li>
<li>Secure SAHARA Get Web interfaces for portals</li>
</ul>

<p class="subhead">
1.0 Sahara release in production for LOREnet
<ul>
<li>Harvester based on the DAREnet harvester.</li>
</ul>
</p>
